      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and minor dings, though the paint still maintains a decent overall appearance. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some fading from sun exposure, but all major components remain intact. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, having been kept up with basic maintenance, though it may require some minor suspension work or fluid refreshes in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over a showroom finish.",
