    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and the paint is still glowing. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love!",
