    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This example features the highly sought-after 3.8L DFI flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Equipped with PASM active damping and a factory limited-slip differential, the chassis remains taut and responsive, mirroring its original factory specifications. The exterior retains its deep, original luster with zero evidence of track use or mechanical fatigue. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this naturally aspirated icon offers a pure, visceral driving experience in a condition that satisfies the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
